{
  "stem": "24111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was shipped to Germany, not for our consumption.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how-- how long did this last in Villa Emma?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Villa Emma lasted [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] quite a long time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It lasted till the British and American forces started to land in Anzio.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it changed in the moment when Mussolini was-- had to abdicate, and Marshal Badoglio took over the government of the-- of Italy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The King Emmanuel was just a figurehead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Badoglio tried to make peace or armistice, with the British and American forces.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the Germans were against it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started to occupy Italy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They liberated Mussolini from Gran Sasso.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came down the boot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They came down from Austria.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They actually occupied Italy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A lot of Italian soldiers tried to escape, tried to go underground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And our camp, our Villa Emma, at that time, was requested as a headquarters or as an building for the German occupying forces.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But before I come to that, I would like to tell you that Joschko established contact, with the cloister and the church in Nonantola, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and with one of the doctors, which came occasionally to our children when they had colds or not really serious sicknesses.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he came, Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Bocari.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when we had to leave Nonantola, it was rather sudden.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we had to leave Villa Emma, it was rather sudden.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the German, as well as the fascists, knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because-- I don't know if I told you before-- the Italian government, the fascistic Italian government, partially supported our group, financially.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was an internment camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Villa Emma was an-- a camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a villa.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had no-- we-- we had-- were restricted in movement.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
